author: Universal Pictures
description: As the Property Master on The Woman in the Yard, Cheri Rodrigo knows that props aren’t just objects, they’re storytelling tools that help build characters and have the potential to become lasting cinematic iconography! Through her work selecting and designing props, Cheri proves that passion, networking (and a little love for on-set chaos) can go a long way. Catch #thewomanintheyard in theaters now! #makeituniversal #myuniversalstory
title: My Universal Story: Cheri Rodrigo | THE WOMAN IN THE YARD

author: Universal Pictures
description:
Nicola Jackson’s journey into film started with a single moment, stepping onto a set as a teenager and realizing it was where she belonged. Now as 3rd AD on Drop, she’s keeping the cast and crew in sync and making every scene run smoothly.

Her story is a reminder that breaking into the film industry isn’t just about luck— it’s about persistence, passion, and showing up every day ready to make things happen. 💫 See the results of her hard work on the big screen. Drop is now playing in theaters! 🎬 #makeituniversal #myuniversalstory #dropthemovie
title: My Universal Story: Nicola Jackson | DROP
